### ============= Authentication =============

### Register a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "niilo@example.com",
  "username": "niilo",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=niilo%40example.com&password=password123

### Get current user (requires token from login)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============= Example Endpoint =============

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/example/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Niilo",
  "task": "Test my API"
}

### ============= LLM Summarization =============

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/llm/summarize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "This is a long text that should be summarized. Add your text here."
}

### ============= Health Checks =============

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/metrics